   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.680", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach den doch mehrheitlich konstruktiven Reden meiner Vorredner wird es Sie nicht \u00fcberraschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.760", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch ich hier einen eher positiven Ton anschlagen werde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.200", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Mittel aus dem ERP-Sonderverm\u00f6gen sind Grundlage der Mittelstandsf\u00f6rderung durch die KfW. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der vorliegende Wirtschaftsplan ist eine Fortschreibung dieser Arbeit\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.360", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit einer gro\u00dfen Neuerung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.240", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
