   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.120", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht nur in der Gr\u00fcndungsphase stehen Unternehmerinnen und Unternehmer regelm\u00e4\u00dfig vor besonderen Investitionsbedarfen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sei es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.720", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um innovative Produkte und Dienstleistungen zu entwickeln und zur Marktreife zu bringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sei es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um ressourcenschonende Produktionsmittel anzuschaffen oder um die Unternehmensnachfolge zu regeln oder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.200", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei haben sie im internationalen Wettbewerb um Finanzmittel einen gro\u00dfen Nachteil: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
